Seminars
OMSCS also periodically offers seminars. Seminars are one credit hour, graded pass/fail, and do not count toward foundational or graduation requirements. Specific details about what seminars are available in a particular semester are sent to the omscs-official email list during Phase II registration.

To see a history of what seminars have been available, check out the Seminars page.